window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Samantha</b></p> <p>I had the perfect life; a husband who loved me and two kids who were my world. But then someone else answered his phone, and my perfect life shattered. When he died, I was left with answers he couldn't give me and a box full of lies. He left me broken.</p> <p><b>Blake</b></p> <p>I fell in love when I was 15, knowing she was the one. </p> <p>For five years, she was my everything - my every breath, every heartbeat, every thought. She made me promise to move on and love again, but I broke those promises because I can't move on.</p> <p>Two broken souls are brought together by tragedy and heartbreak. Can a broken love story be fixed?</p>"; 
